  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>LogTargetStandardOut</TypeRef> constructor creates a target that writes messages to <TypeRef>std::cout</TypeRef>.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Usage">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[LogTargetStandardOut(bool flushAfterOutput);]]></Code>
    <SubSection Title="Argument list">
      <ArgumentList>
        <ArgumentListEntry Type="bool" Name="flushAfterOutput">If <TypeRef>true</TypeRef>, the target flushes <TypeRef>std::cout</TypeRef> after every message.</ArgumentListEntry>
      </ArgumentList>
    </SubSection>
  </Section>
